channel.title: Yes another leaving thread....Me
channel.description:
As many people have left the RS cheating scene, I feel that it is my time to do so as well. I've been around just about EVERY big RS cheating site for 2-3 years now, and I guess a lot of you guys know me. I don't really know why, but I've just simply lost interest in scripting, cheating on Runescape, and RS all together. I've just found interest in other things on the computer.
I was spending [B][U]WAY[/U][/B] too much time on the computer every day, and I need to have some self control and stop. School will be starting here in 5 days and I feel that it will be better to just stop now, before I be stupid and don't concentrate enough on sports/school work/girls(:D) because of the computer.
You still might see me around in some of my favorite threads, or if I happen to see an interesting thread now and then. And I'll pop in at a few other forums as well, but for the most part I'm outta here guys. Now as I've seen it happen [U]plenty[/U] of times, I know I won't be able to stay away forever, so I'll be back eventually most likely. Once a cheater, always a cheater!
Thanks tons to everyone thats ever done anything for me, and you special people know who you are. I've learned soooo much about the computer and everything while I've been at these sites. Hope RS cheating keeps going strong, and good luck to you guys, I've really and truly enjoyed it ;)
[B]~Mjordan~[/B]
